description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. 3D images magically appear before your eyes as you gaze at seemingly random designs.  A collection of 70 Magic Images that will amaze and delight you - if you can see them.  Will you be able to see the Magic Images, or will they leave you cross-eyed?
